<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.IRenderer.CreateShaderProgram" Title="CreateShaderProgram method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IRenderer">IRenderer</PageRef> ->
    CreateShaderProgram
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>CreateShaderProgram</TypeRef> method constructs and returns a new object which implements the <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IShaderProgram">IShaderProgram</PageRef>
      interface.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[IShaderProgram::unique_ptr CreateShaderProgram();]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="IShaderProgram!cobalt.graphics.IShaderProgram">
        A freshly constructed <TypeRef>IShaderProgram</TypeRef> object, wrapped in a <TypeRef>unique_ptr</TypeRef>.
      </ReturnValue>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
